---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import bgMap from '@imgs/map-what-we.png';

import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
import Membership from "../members/membership.astro";
const orphansDetails = await getCollection("orphans");
---
<section class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 lg:grid-cols-6 lg:gap-8 py-20 px-24">
    <div class="w-11/12 mx-auto lg:col-span-4 bg-center bg-no-repeat" style={{ backgroundImage: `url(${bgMap.src})` }}>
        <h2 class="lora italic text-[35px] font-bold leading-[45px] uppercase">What <br /><small class="text-[30px] inline-block text-black capitalize">We are doing?</small></h2>
        <hr class="border-1 border-primary w-44 my-3" />
        <h6 class="font-bold lora italic my-2">
            We helped {orphansDetails.reduce((sum, orphan) => sum + Number(orphan.data.total), 0).toLocaleString()} orphans, across 166 districts in the country, ensuring that vulnerable children are not left behind.
        </h6>
        <p class="text-gray-500">
            With 44 dedicated orphanages operated by member organizations, POCF is creating a safe and nurturing environment for these children, empowering them to build brighter futures and break the cycle of poverty. 6,837 orphans have reached the milestone of pursuing college and university education, reflecting POCFâ€™s commitment to nurturing future leaders.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-9 gap-6 py-6 px-3 lora italic">
            <div class="flex flex-col col-span-3">
                <Icon name="books" class="text-primary w-10 h-auto" />
                <h4 class="font-bold text-2xl">Education</h4>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-500">We believe every orphan deserves the opportunity to thrive through quality education, empowering them to build a brighter future.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col col-span-3">
                <Icon name="heartplus" class="text-primary w-10 h-auto" />
                <h4 class="font-bold text-2xl">Health</h4>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-500">Our goal is to ensure every child enjoys good health and well-being, laying the foundation for a happy and fulfilling life.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col col-span-3">
                <Icon name="food" class="text-primary w-10 h-auto" />
                <h4 class="font-bold text-2xl">Care & Support</h4>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-500">Our Orphan Care & Family Support program addresses families' immediate needs, providing vital assistance to ensure stability and hope for vulnerable children and their caregivers</p>
            </div>                        
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-primary/80 px-4 lg:px-8 py-3 lg:col-span-2 mx-2 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-8 text-2xl lato">
        <h3 class="text-white leading-[35px] font-[600]">POCF has emerged as a strong and impactful platform, significantly transforming the lives of orphans across Pakistan. <span class="text-secondary font-[800]"> <span class="counter">
            {orphansDetails.reduce((sum, orphan) => sum + Number(orphan.data.total), 0).toLocaleString()}    
        </span> orphans under its care, 20-reputable INGOs/NGOs part of this forum.</span></h3>
        <div class="flex flex-row gap-3 font-bold text-[11px]">
            <button class="make-member-button uppercase bg-secondary text-white hover:text-secondary hover:bg-white py-2 px-4">Join Us!</button> 
            <Membership />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>